properties.entry:
Executes the specified command iteratively n times.
	Syntax: for [min] [max] command {args}
	You can specify a '%s' as a parameter to use the index of the cycle.

Saves current state.
{path} is the path and file name where to save the file, e.g. ~/.rgrpg/session.dat
save {path}

Loads previously saved state.
{path} is the path and file name where to load the file, e.g. ~/.rgrpg/session.dat
load {path}
